=head1 DESCRIPTION

Specifies criteria for sorting the results of a request for findings.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AttributeName => Str

The name of the property to sort the results by. Valid values are:
count, createdAt, policyDetails.action.apiCallDetails.firstSeen,
policyDetails.action.apiCallDetails.lastSeen, resourcesAffected,
severity.score, type, and updatedAt.


=head2 OrderBy => Str

The sort order to apply to the results, based on the value for the
property specified by the attributeName property. Valid values are:
ASC, sort the results in ascending order; and, DESC, sort the results
in descending order.



